---
title: Chicken & Mushroom Orzotto with Rocket
description: A twist on the Italian classic, this risotto-style recipe is made with velvety orzo pasta instead of rice and is full of fresh flavours perfect for this colder evenings. With just 15 minutes hands on cooking time, this is a great alternative for getting the same comforting results of a risotto, without the arm work! We’ll send your compliments to the chef!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-mushroom-orzotto-6de17907-9586f61b.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/chicken-mushroom-orzotto-5af57a6dae08b514452c5702-42d8c021.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/chicken-mushroom-orzotto-5af57a6dae08b514452c5702
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: Italian
